  "detailed_description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7985aaf2f7260d2f159a40dec0f1b1c0.poster.avif?t=1738863827\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7985aaf2f7260d2f159a40dec0f1b1c0.webm?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7985aaf2f7260d2f159a40dec0f1b1c0.mp4?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bloodbound is a fast-paced, Vampire multiplayer shooter that pits you and your friends against another team of players in an all-out battle to the death. Players must choose a side and fight till the bloody end, battling it out in a variety of locales. With a wide list of fearless characters, players can decide between the quick-witted and talented Slayers or the demons of the night themselves, the Vampires.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7b1334ba864f2e8de4d91cef7b213bdd.poster.avif?t=1738863827\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7b1334ba864f2e8de4d91cef7b213bdd.webm?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7b1334ba864f2e8de4d91cef7b213bdd.mp4?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As a Vampire, use Blood Vision to track Slayers, invisibility to hunt or escape, and jump or leap at great distances. Slayers can use telekinetic powers to push vampires away when crowded, cite a prayer to protect you from evil, and much more. Learn to master every character, each of which comes with its own unique weapons and abilities<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/18957297a8a79446644642c24dcc8c19.poster.avif?t=1738863827\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/18957297a8a79446644642c24dcc8c19.webm?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/18957297a8a79446644642c24dcc8c19.mp4?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Players will be able to duke it out on several maps which vary in size and style, from an evacuated, bloody subway station to a cold, terrifying cemetery. Smash through shop fronts and paint the streets red on Blood Avenue or play in a close-quarter environment like Dracula's Castle.",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7985aaf2f7260d2f159a40dec0f1b1c0.poster.avif?t=1738863827\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7985aaf2f7260d2f159a40dec0f1b1c0.webm?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7985aaf2f7260d2f159a40dec0f1b1c0.mp4?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bloodbound is a fast-paced, Vampire multiplayer shooter that pits you and your friends against another team of players in an all-out battle to the death. Players must choose a side and fight till the bloody end, battling it out in a variety of locales. With a wide list of fearless characters, players can decide between the quick-witted and talented Slayers or the demons of the night themselves, the Vampires.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7b1334ba864f2e8de4d91cef7b213bdd.poster.avif?t=1738863827\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7b1334ba864f2e8de4d91cef7b213bdd.webm?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/7b1334ba864f2e8de4d91cef7b213bdd.mp4?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As a Vampire, use Blood Vision to track Slayers, invisibility to hunt or escape, and jump or leap at great distances. Slayers can use telekinetic powers to push vampires away when crowded, cite a prayer to protect you from evil, and much more. Learn to master every character, each of which comes with its own unique weapons and abilities<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/18957297a8a79446644642c24dcc8c19.poster.avif?t=1738863827\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/18957297a8a79446644642c24dcc8c19.webm?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909750/extras/18957297a8a79446644642c24dcc8c19.mp4?t=1738863827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Players will be able to duke it out on several maps which vary in size and style, from an evacuated, bloody subway station to a cold, terrifying cemetery. Smash through shop fronts and paint the streets red on Blood Avenue or play in a close-quarter environment like Dracula's Castle.",
